{"tid":1291363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報指中英聯合聲明無條款容許英國監督一國兩制","createTime":"2019-07-06T23:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T00:40:39.000Z","uid":274789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81a5db772e09970a44d2e14c343974ea4a3460f0","tid":1291363,"uid":274789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:40:00.000Z","msg":"《人民日報》海外版刊登評論文章，批評英國外相侯俊偉等官員，近期多次就香港事務說三道四，要求停止干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，英方官員動輒拿《中英聯合聲明》為插手香港事務製造口實，但實情是聲明中無任何條款，容許英國對香港行使任何權利，亦無賦予英國所謂監督一國兩制的權利。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，中英近年開展務實合作，雙方走向互利共贏的良性發展軌道，英方不應忘記，相互尊重主權領土完整、互不干涉內政，是中英關係基石，奉勸英方某些人應避免損害大局、破壞合作，強調英國必須將香港作為中國一部分來對待，兩國才能夠得以開展對話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466882-20190706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466882-20190706.htm&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=689ccaa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466882-20190706.htm&h=b7e73d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466882-20190706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"67add69379fcd1da25ae165cece8aefd3b8b3b3f","tid":1291363,"uid":27670,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:43:19.000Z","msg":"又開始玩文字遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f89142b58f0d4aa76a0d174a2bebd28077d2aaa","tid":1291363,"uid":99365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"又話係歷史文件 依家又話冇條文<br />\n口交部諗定未架"},{"pid":"1d1a38b58728fd3603d5aa630413c632812232cc","tid":1291363,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"賴皮組組長"}]}